---
const points = [
  { dot: 'var(--glow-sky)', title: 'Simple por fuera', desc: 'Links, QR y usernames para acciones normales.' },
  { dot: 'var(--glow-pink)', title: 'Abierta por debajo', desc: 'Infraestructura cripto sin obligarte a vivir en lo técnico.' },
  { dot: 'var(--glow-gold)', title: 'Bajo tu control', desc: 'Puedes enviar, cambiar, activar Earn o retirar cuando quieras.' },
];
---

<section id="control" class="landing-section">
  <div class="landing-shell">
    <div class="split is-reverse" data-reveal>
      <div class="split-visual">
        <div class="stage glow-sky vault-visual" style="margin:0;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 220 220" class="h-[230px] w-[230px]" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
            <g opacity=".9">
              <path d="M106.6 22.1L28 76.8L35.6 82.1L108.3 133.2L181.3 82.5L188.8 77.2L110.4 22.1C109.2 21.4 107.8 21.4 106.6 22.1Z" fill="#A7D4DE"/>
              <path d="M110 139.8C108.9 140.5 107.7 140.5 106.7 139.8L34.5 89.7L27.9 85.1L27.8 114.7L34.4 119.3L108.2 170.6L182.1 119.7L188.7 115.1L188.8 85.6L182.2 90.1L110 139.8Z" fill="#DEA6BC"/>
              <path d="M109.9 177.1C108.9 177.8 107.6 177.8 106.6 177.1L34.4 127L27.8 122.4L27.8 152L34.3 156.6L108.1 207.9L182 157L188.6 152.4L188.7 122.9L182.1 127.4L109.9 177.1Z" fill="#DED9A6"/>
            </g>
            <path class="vault-shield" d="M110 72L150 91V126C150 156 110 174 110 174C110 174 70 156 70 126V91L110 72Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,.07)" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path class="check-path" d="M92 124L105 137L131 106" stroke="#9CE3F4" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="split-copy">
        <span class="section-eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-num">08</span><span class="eyebrow-sep"></span>Control del usuario</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Tu dinero sigue siendo tuyo.</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">
          Parmelia es 100% onchain: aquí tu dinero sí te pertenece a ti, y no a nosotros.
        </p>

        <div class="point-list" data-reveal-stagger>
          {points.map((point) => (
            <div class="point-row">
              <span class="dot" style={`background:${point.dot}; color:${point.dot};`}></span>
              <p><strong style="color:var(--color-text); font-weight:600;">{point.title}.</strong> {point.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <p class="microcopy" style="text-align:left; margin:6px 0 0;">
          Lo técnico existe debajo. La experiencia no tiene que parecer técnica.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
